Scope of this license:

This license covers the ECCO Master Context Public Edition
specification text and accompanying typographic and visual
artifacts in this repository. The Master Context is an
archival reference work: a doctrinal architecture specification
intended to be read, cited, and linked, but not adapted or
repackaged. ND is therefore deliberate.

ECCO operates this repository under a public-research posture
for its diagnostic and educational surfaces (such as this
Master Context) and a closed posture for its commercial and
revenue-generating surfaces. The visibility of this repository
reflects that posture; it is not an invitation to repackage,
resell, or otherwise capture the work for purposes that do not
credit or sustain its source.

Per the structural-replicability doctrine in §J of the
specification, the architecture is intentionally inspectable.
The license restrictions above govern reproduction and
adaptation of this document; they do not impair another firm's
right to operate their own architecture using whatever frame
they author themselves.

