Version history of this license file:

  Initial commit of master-context — CC BY-NC-ND 4.0,
  inherited from the LICENSE template authored for the ECCO
  Scanner (scan.etherealconnectionsco.com).

  v1.0 of Master Context onward — CC BY-NC-ND 4.0, with
  Attribution string corrected from "ECCO Scanner" to
  "ECCO Master Context" and the Scope section re-authored
  for this artifact's purpose.

The license class (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0) is retained because the
Master Context is the default-case archival reference work
the ECCO Deploy Playbook §2.1 identifies as fitting BY-NC-ND.
The substitution was attribution-string only; the legal terms
are unchanged. Per Deploy Playbook §6.2 (Template-inherited
license contradicting artifact purpose), this audit was
performed at first deploy.

